---
group_count: 37
atr1_unknown: 4
entries:
  "0000":
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - text: 他們？
  "0001":
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - text: 傳說之劍？
  "0002":
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - text: 再見
  "0003":
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - text: 其實……
  FR01_Talk_01:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr01
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 42
      - text: "我受夠了～\n拜託救救我！！"
  FR01_Talk_02:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr01
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 18
      - text: 難道……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n我得救了？"
      - control:
          kind: single_choice
          label: 3
  FR01_Talk_03:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr01
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "格瑪納很不可靠，\n要是你沒來的話……\n真不知道我會變成怎樣……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 9
      - text: 謝謝你。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "不過……\n旅行還真危險呢……\n雜誌上根本沒提到這種事啊……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "唉……看來凡事都是\n不經一事不長一智呢。"
  FR01_Talk_04:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr01
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: 你說格瑪納？
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n他一看到怪物跑出來，\n就一溜煙地自己先逃走了。\n竟然丟下女孩子逃跑，\n你不覺得很過分嗎？\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound2
          unknown:
            - 12
            - 205
      - text: "我絕對不會原諒他！\n\n你說他在格魯德峽谷驛站對吧？"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n我要去教訓他！"
  FR01_Talk_05:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr01
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 4
      - text: "只要想到萬一你沒來救我……\n現在我都還會發抖，真的很謝謝你。"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 不過……旅行還真危險呢……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n雜誌上根本沒提到這種事啊……\n看來凡事都是\n不經一事不長一智呢。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 但也多虧這樣才讓我明白，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n自己並不適合出來旅行。\n因此我在這裡稍作休息之後，\n就打算回家了。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 9
      - text: "你還會繼續旅行吧？\n你很強，我想應該沒問題，但還是要小心哦。"
  FR02_Talk_01:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr02
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 2
            - 14
      - text: "可惡……\n這群臭豬怪竟敢得意忘形……"
  FR02_Talk_02:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr02
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "謝謝你救了我。\n唉，真是有夠衰的。"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: "啊～全身都痛到不行，\n那群臭豬怪真是太可惡了！"
      - control:
          kind: single_choice
          label: 3
  FR02_Talk_03:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr02
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "我原本想讓格瑪納\n瞧瞧我有多憤怒的……\n但是他一看到我，\n就快哭出來似的……\n我看他自己好像也很怕\n同伴不回來了……\n所以也無可奈何，\n只好原諒他了。"
  FR02_Talk_04:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr02
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: "你說格瑪納？\n\n他竟然不來救我，\n自己躲在驛站逍遙自在……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n我也要讓他嚐嚐\n我受到的痛苦！"
  FR02_Talk_05:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr02
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "我原本想讓格瑪納\n瞧瞧我有多憤怒的……\n但是他一看到我，\n就快哭出來似的……\n所以也無可奈何，\n只好原諒他了。\n不過我……已經不想\n再成為別人的包袱了。\n因此打算讓旅程在此暫告一段落。\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 0
      - text: "等變得像你一樣強之後，\n我會重新踏上旅程的。\n下次有緣再相遇時，\n就換我來保護你。\n你就好好期待吧。"
  FR03_Talk_01:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr03
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 42
      - text: "我會死嗎……\n人生要在此結束了嗎……\n嗚嗚……要是跟格瑪納前輩一樣強，\n我就能輕易打垮這些傢伙了……"
  FR03_Talk_02:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr03
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 4
            - 21
      - text: 奇怪……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 我……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 10
      - text: 還活著？
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n我還活著耶？\n是你幫忙打倒怪物的嗎？"
  FR03_Talk_03:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr03
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 我問格瑪納前輩……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n「為什麼沒來救我？」\n然後……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n前輩說了一堆"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 傳說之劍
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "\n怎樣怎樣的來呼嚨我……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "格瑪納前輩……\n該不會其實很弱吧……"
  FR03_Talk_04:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr03
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 0
      - text: "好厲害！\n\n你好厲害！\n\n你的實力應該\n僅次於格瑪納前輩吧！"
      - control:
          kind: single_choice
          label: 3
  FR03_Talk_05:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr03
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 4
            - 20
      - text: "咦……格瑪納前輩\n人在驛站嗎？\n他沒來救我嗎？\n\n沒武器所以沒辦法？\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 6
      - text: "咦？你在說什麼啊？\n前輩可是手刀專家，空手也很強耶……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 難不成……我被騙了嗎？
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n我、我去跟前輩確認一下！"
  FR03_Talk_06:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr03
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 我問格瑪納前輩……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n「為什麼沒來救我？」\n然後……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n前輩說了一堆"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 傳說之劍
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "\n怎樣怎樣的來呼嚨我……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "雖然只是我個人的猜測……但格瑪納前輩……\n該不會其實是個膽小鬼吧。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 18
      - text: "不過我發現最膽小的人，\n是一直依賴前輩的自己。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "所以我決定今後不再依賴任何人，\n要試著獨自前進。\n然後我會努力試著成為\n足以讓他人依賴的人。"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 0
      - text: ……就像你一樣。
  FR04_Talk_01:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr04
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 32
      - text: 這、
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 這裡很危險……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n快、快、快、"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 快退下……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
  FR04_Talk_02:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr04
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 10
            - 11
      - text: "好、好棒的身手！\n你是哪個流派的？"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 24
      - text: "抱、抱歉，\n看你這麼強，在下忍不住興奮起來了。\n在下名叫貝倪。\n\n雖然在下對武術多少有些研究，\n但跟同伴在一起時突然遇襲……\n而且還用寡不敵眾這種極為卑劣的手段，\n讓我進退維谷。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 13
      - text: "要是你沒經過，\n真不知會怎樣……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 哎呀，真是不勝感激……
      - control:
          kind: single_choice
          label: 3
  FR04_Talk_03:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr04
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 13
      - text: "看到格瑪納閣下後，\n大概是終於安心了，腳突然抖了起來。\n看來在下的修行\n還有待加強呢。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 5
            - 4
      - text: "話說你的身手……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "根本能與大災厄之際，\n那名驍勇善戰的劍士大人匹敵嘛～"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n哈哈！"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n談論約100年前的傳說也沒什麼用～\n總之在下會暫時\n在此稍作休息。"
  FR04_Talk_04:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr04
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 4
            - 23
      - text: 格瑪納閣下嗎？
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 24
      - text: "太好了。\n格瑪納閣下沒事啊。"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n在下會火速前往\n格魯德峽谷驛站。"
  FR04_Talk_05:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004_fr04
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 24
      - text: "你的身手……\n\n根本能與大災厄之際，\n那名驍勇善戰的劍士大人匹敵嘛～"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n哈哈！"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n談論約100年前的傳說也沒什麼用～\n不過在下仍是半吊子一事，\n則是擺在眼前、無法撼動之事實……\n所以在下打算從頭開始修行。\n\n雖然這趟旅程在此結束，\n但在下很感激能認識你。"
  Npc_oasis004_100:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "你……\n\n有看到我的同伴嗎？\n\n分別是名叫"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 貝倪、阿邁尼、娜塔內、帕穆
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "的\n四個旅行者……"
  Npc_oasis004_101:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "你知道相傳在海拉魯森林，\n有把等待主人出現的"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 傳說之劍
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "嗎？\n既然都被稱為傳說了，\n我想那把劍一定超強的。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "要是有那把劍，\n根本就不用怕怪物了。"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n但實際上怎麼可能有那種東西呢……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "所以說……\n\n要是你有找到他們，\n可以幫忙告訴他們我在這裡等著嗎？\n他們的名字叫\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 貝倪、阿邁尼、娜塔內、帕穆
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "。\n要是有看到他們，\n就麻煩你了。"
  Npc_oasis004_102:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: "我想……也是……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 6
            - 1
      - text: "我跟他們\n一起出來旅行。\n卻在"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 梅竹台地的街道一帶
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "\n突然遇到怪物……\n我一心只想逃，就跑到這裡來……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 16
      - text: 可是……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n當我回頭一看……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n大家……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n大家全不見了……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 1
      - text: "難不成是被怪物給……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "不，大家一定都沒事的。\n\n所以我才會在這裡，\n等著大家回來。\n如果你有在這附近的街道\n找到他們……\n可以幫忙告訴他們\n格瑪納在這裡等著嗎？"
  Npc_oasis004_103:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 16
      - text: "我那些同伴名叫\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 貝倪、阿邁尼、娜塔內、帕穆
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "。\n要是你有找到他們，\n可以幫忙告訴他們我在這裡等著嗎？"
  Npc_oasis004_104:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 16
      - text: 果然是在
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 梅竹台地
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "一帶\n受到怪物襲擊了嗎……\n我是很想去救他們啦……\n\n但是我……\n身上又沒帶什麼武器……\n如果有"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 傳說之劍
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "之類的，\n就能痛扁怪物了。"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 1
            - 2
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 1
          unknown: 6
  Npc_oasis004_105:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 16
      - text: 唉……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
  Npc_oasis004_106:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 2
      - text: "喂，我都聽說囉。\n\n是小哥從怪物手中\n救出我的同伴對吧？\n你真厲害呢！！\n\n聽說你在很窄的木橋上\n痛扁怪物們一頓。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 要是我也有
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 傳說之劍
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "，\n就能跟你一起戰鬥了。"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 1
            - 2
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 1
          unknown: 6
  Npc_oasis004_107:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "你知道相傳在海拉魯森林，\n有把等待主人出現的"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 傳說之劍
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "嗎？\n既然都被稱為傳說了，\n我想那把劍一定超強的。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "要是有那把劍，\n根本就不用怕怪物了。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 但我怎麼可能會有啦……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
  Npc_oasis004_108:
    attributes: NPC_oasis004
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: "我想……\n\n其他同伴一定也\n受到怪物襲擊了。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 要是……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
